@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: User Edit Profile

actor User
participant "Frontend/UI (React)" as UI
participant "Backend/API" as API
participant "Auth Middleware (JWT)" as AUTH
database "Database (Neon)" as DB

User -> UI: Open Profile Page
UI -> API: GET /user/profile (JWT)
API -> AUTH: Verify token
AUTH --> API: Valid
API -> DB: Fetch user by ID
DB --> API: User data
API --> UI: Return profile
UI --> User: Display profile

User -> UI: Click "Edit"
UI -> UI: Enable form fields

User -> UI: Click "Save"
UI -> API: PATCH /user/profile (updated data + JWT)

API -> AUTH: Verify token
AUTH --> API: Valid
API -> DB: Update user record
DB --> API: Success
API --> UI: 200 OK

UI -> API: GET /user/profile (refetch)
API -> DB: Fetch updated user
DB --> API
API --> UI: Updated profile

UI --> User: Show success toast + display updated data

@enduml